name: Supreme Star Card Master
summary: On Blue Sea Star, there exists a transcendent group that controls various unimaginable powers through armed cards, known as  Star Card Masters.Su Yuan had transmigrated, bringing along a system that could enhance his own Star Cards.Awakening of the Transformation Realm Soul Awakening Card = Top-Tier Talent Soul Card "Azure Sky Phoenix"Perfect Level Wind Walking: Evades certain ranged attacks!Perfect Level Gray Flame Strike: Twin Gray Flame Strikes in unison!Perfect Level Elemental Magnetism Pressure: Gravity Domain!Perfect Level Space Cut: Boundary Breaking Line!Perfect Steel Flame Finger + Perfect Hardened Iron Armor = Golden Burning Hand!...Starting from enhancing his initial Soul Awakening Card, Su Yuan gradually ascended to the ultimate realm of Star Card Masters!
author: Cloud Camellia
